{"tid":1946790,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[超突發聲援] 3月28號法庭聲援（懇請大家抽空出席）","createTime":"2020-03-28T00:00:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T02:29:02.000Z","uid":292499,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"60356c0a7c83172d63a8395c4d7019d5514715e4","tid":1946790,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T00:00:14.000Z","msg":"🛑🛑🛑🛑‼️緊急聲援表‼️🛑🛑🛑🛑<br />\n<br />\n🏛九龍城裁判法院<br />\n襲警（詳情後補）<br />\n<br />\n►--- 09:30 am ---◄<br />\n🏛東區裁判法院第一庭<br />\n<strong>#0326 小西灣子彈案 </strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200328/mobile/bkn-20200328064417286-0328_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200328%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200328064417286-0328_00822_001.html&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3fiEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=ec8e331e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200328/mobile/bkn-20200328064417286-0328_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"8878586c06b10dea6bf7399a7384efa0a5086600","tid":1946790,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T00:00:28.000Z","msg":"#聲援注意 #旁聽須知 #遮陣接送<br />\n⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️<br />\n以下為法庭旁聽須知要點，十分重要，請大家旁聽前睇睇，唔好留壞印象比法官。<br />\n<br />\n1⃣👨&zwj;👩&zwj;👧&zwj;👦旁聽須知<br />\n➖請預早開庭前15-30分鐘到所屬樓層排隊取籌🔖<br />\n➖法院大樓不能拍照 / 攝影📷<br />\n➖法庭範圍內保持安靜，切勿喧嘩🗣勿嗌口號<br />\n➖手機請轉為靜音/關機，亦部份法官不容許法庭內使用手機<br />\n➖遲到/已開庭，庭內未滿亦可進入，進出請向法官鞠躬<br />\n➖庭內不能戴帽，入庭前請除帽<br />\n➖部份法官不容許戴口罩<br />\n➖庭內不準飲食<br />\n➖主要以英語進行審訊，不清楚可以睇我哋嘅文字直播台 @youarenotalonehk_live<br />\n➖高等法院大樓1樓至14樓，需在地下進行安檢；低層4樓法庭的人士，則需在低層4樓進行安檢；低層3樓至地下，並不需要接受保安檢查<br />\n<br />\n法院禮儀請參閱：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcfa.hk/tc/visiting/attending/other/etiquette/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcfa.hk%2Ftc%2Fvisiting%2Fattending%2Fother%2Fetiquette%2Findex.html&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3fiEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=90ebe422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcfa.hk/tc/visiting/attending/other/etiquette/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2⃣💝貼心提示：<br />\n拘捕後直接過堂嘅手足，袋可能被狗仔咬爛咗，大家見到不妨遞個有色膠袋或者環保袋比佢哋啦<br />\n<br />\n3⃣☔️遮陣接送<br />\n保釋處理：將由正門離開，保釋手續需時，請耐心等候，可幫手足call定的士， 遮陣接送手足亦可先向家屬溝通， 避免誤會<br />\n<br />\n4⃣🚓還押送車<br />\n還押處理手足，將由側門 / 停車場離開，可等懲教車送車<br />\nP.S. 懲教不是POPO唔好屌佢哋"},{"pid":"d81e4a7cd29a835062ee0af3b1f2abea9958ffe8","tid":1946790,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T00:00:38.000Z","msg":"詳情可follow被捕人士關注組<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3fiEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=6c0f026d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk</a><br />\n<br />\nIG<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/youarenotalonehk?igshid=knzk6gr75kea\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fyouarenotalonehk%3Figshid%3Dknzk6gr75kea&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3fiEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=1d7bc903\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/youarenotalonehk?igshid=knzk6gr75kea</a>"},{"pid":"08ce7a4ee323b1023ca2a302c99f51dbcdd6eaaa","tid":1946790,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T00:00:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3KL2uoe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3KL2uoe.jpg&h=96935d65&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db35c265294bd2d5d816789813e8e73fd8237760","tid":1946790,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T00:01:10.000Z","msg":"【司法機關政務處公告】- 11/02/2020<br />\n<br />\n基於公共衞生的考慮，由 2020 年 2 月 13 日起司法機構 將實施以下安排:-<br />\n<br />\n<strong>體溫檢測</strong><br />\n- 所有人均須接受體溫檢測<br />\n- 發燒或拒絕接受檢測人士不得進入<br />\n<br />\n<strong>法庭座位安排</strong><br />\n- 公眾席的座位數目將減少約一半<br />\n- 取消站立旁聽聆訊<br />\n- 將會使用較大的法庭，並在可行情況下進行廣播"},{"pid":"bad339c1cd7a77ce6f5e67453cbd044a85b75613","tid":1946790,"uid":93962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T00:01:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d147698d0831ebe36d43816f55467879705f125e","tid":1946790,"uid":83990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T00:01:22.000Z","msg":"P"},{"pid":"4a1659ed800c28c06228f6f2347a5bfaea87ed9c","tid":1946790,"uid":83990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T00:01:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29798ce96b2c99577db96a58df19470b47a3c100","tid":1946790,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T00:01:44.000Z","msg":"#上庭聲援 #交通資訊 <br />\n九龍城裁判法院交通：<br />\n於「九龍城警署」(西行)/「香港眼科醫院」(東行)巴士站落車<br />\n<strong>新界：</strong><br />\n將軍澳：98C,296C,796C<br />\n新界其餘各區未有直達交通<br />\n<br />\n<strong>九龍：</strong><br />\n啟德、九龍城：20<br />\n大角咀：13D,16,20<br />\n彩雲：9<br />\n九龍灣：2A,13D,16<br />\n觀塘、藍田：16<br />\n慈雲山：203E<br />\n油尖旺：9<br />\n美孚、深水埗：2A<br />\n<br />\n<strong>交通資訊由【抗爭行動交通頻道】提供</strong>"},{"pid":"250927f9459f48513289bd71061bdd8870c7165f","tid":1946790,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T00:02:09.000Z","msg":"#上庭聲援 #交通資訊 <br />\n東區裁判法院交通：<br />\n於「西灣河（嘉亨灣）巴士總站」落車<br />\n<strong>九龍</strong><br />\n啟德：608<br />\n<strong>港島</strong><br />\n中環、金鐘：720<br />\nCWB、天后、北角、太古：2<br />\n柴灣、赤柱：14<br />\n<br />\n於「鯉魚灣」巴士站落車<br />\n<strong>港島：</strong><br />\n中環：722<br />\nCWB、天后：2A,2X,77<br />\n北角、太古：2A,77,99,722<br />\n筲箕灣：2X,77,99<br />\n香港仔：77<br />\n海怡：99<br />\n<br />\n另外「西灣河碼頭」<br />\n有船來往觀塘碼頭，但旁邊係水警總部<br />\n<br />\n<strong>交通資訊由【抗爭行動交通頻道】提供</strong>"},{"pid":"5190ee864210e35de2382c5db7edbc9e88d6df07","tid":1946790,"uid":83990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T00:02:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e7b60868f9bb7a5dd49a6ed1496467af0c4e862","tid":1946790,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T00:02:38.000Z","msg":"九龍城、東區要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" clas